    {
      "type": "thought",
      "text": "The user is experiencing a Windows Blue Screen of Death (BSOD) with the stop code \"WHEA_UNCORRECTABLE_ERROR\". They've had this at least a couple times yesterday. They want me to:\n\n1. Investigate using proper enterprise root cause analysis\n2. Tell them its fixability score using iFix (I think they mean some scoring system)\n3. Tell how reliable it is\n4. Whether they can improve their PC temperature\n5. Check if components are okay\n6. Don't want to stress test components\n7. Just want a decent assessment using PowerShell/Python tools\n\nI need to be in plan mode - read-only. I should research the issue and create a plan. Let me first search for information about WHEA_UNCORRECTABLE_ERROR to understand what it is and what causes it.\n\nLet me also check what tools are available on the system - PowerShell, Python, etc.",
      "timestamp": 1783146291717
    },
