      "output": "Title: Certificati e Attestati Tecnico Informatico - Italia in Digitale\nURL: https://grow.google/intl/it/google-career-certificates/it-support/\nPublished: N/A\nAuthor: N/A\nHighlights:\n# Google Career Certificate in IT Support\n...\nPreparati a una nuova carriera nell'assistenza informatica e impara a risolvere i problemi dati dalla tecnologia. Scopri come fornire un servizio clienti eccellente nell'ambito hardware, Internet o software. Dopo aver completato il certificato IT Support, è possibile approfondire il settore con il certificato di Google IT Automation with Python, disponibile in inglese.\n...\nCandidati per la posizione di IT Support Technician, Help Desk Technician, IT Specialist e molto altro.\n...\nCompleta il certificato online al ritmo che preferisci in meno di 6 mesi.\n...\nFai notare il tuo CV con Google Career Certificate, sviluppato da esperti di Google.\n\n---\n\nTitle: Google IT Support Professional Certificate - Coursera\nURL: https://www.coursera.org/professional-certificates/google-it-support\nPublished: N/A\nAuthor: N/A\nHighlights:\nThe launchpad to a career in IT. This program is designed to take beginner learners to job readiness in about three-to-six months.\n\n---\n\nTitle: Google IT Support Professional Certificate | Coursera\nURL: https://www.coursera.org/professional-certificates/google-it-support?adgroupid=88979276353&adposition=&campaignid=1855233775&creativeid=408459231277&device=c&devicemodel=&hide_mobile_promo=&keyword=&matchtype=&network=g\nPublished: N/A\nAuthor: N/A\nHighlights:\nGoogle IT Support Professional Certificate | Coursera\n...\n## Google IT Support Professional Certificate\n...\n# Google IT Support Professional Certificate\n...\nThe launchpad to a career in IT.\n...\nThis program is designed to take beginner learners to job readiness in about three-to-six months.\n...\nInstructor: Google Career Certificates\n...\n## What you'll learn\n...\nLearn to perform\n...\n-to-\n...\ncomputer assembly,\n...\nTaught in English\n...\n6 languages available\n...\n## Professional Certificate - 6 course seriesNew AI skills\n...\nPrepare for a career in the high-growth field of IT, no experience or degree required. Get professional training designed by Google and get on the fast-track to a competitively paid job. There are over 287,000 open jobs in IT support with a median entry-level salary of $70,000 in the U.S.¹\n...\nGoogle Career Certificates\n\n---\n\nTitle: Launch an IT Support Career | Get Job-Ready - Grow with Google\nURL: https://grow.google/certificates/it-support/\nPublished: N/A\nAuthor: N/A\nHighlights:\nGoogle's IT Support Certificate Training Program includes use cases for AI tools, preparing you for an entry-level IT support job.\n\n---\n\nTitle: Google Career Certificate in IT Support - UPA - Utenti Pubblicità associati\nURL: https://www.upa.it/it/google-career-certificate-in-it-support.html\nPublished: N/A\nAuthor: N/A\nHighlights:\nGoogle Career Certificate in IT Support - UPA - Utenti Pubblicità associati\n...\nIl percorso in IT Support di Google Career Certificates consentirà ai partecipanti di:\n...\n- Acquisire le competenze necessarie per avere successo in un lavoro IT di livello base - Imparare a svolgere le attività quotidiane di supporto IT tra cui l'assemblaggio del computer, la messa a punto di una rete wireless, l'installazione di programmi e il servizio clienti - Scoprire come fornire assistenza clienti end-to-end, dall'identificazione dei problemi alla risoluzione dei problemi e al debug - Imparare a usare i principali sistemi, inclusi Linux, Domain Name Systems, Command-Line Interface e Binary Code",
