      "output": "Title: Google IT Support Professional Certificate - Coursera\nURL: https://www.coursera.org/professional-certificates/google-it-support\nPublished: N/A\nAuthor: N/A\nHighlights:\nTaught in English 6 languages available. Petrobras, TATA, Danone, Capgemini, P&G and L'Oreal\n\n---\n\nTitle: Technical Support Fundamentals | Coursera\nURL: https://www.coursera.org/programs/department-for-communities-avsxy/learn/technical-support-fundamentals?specialization=google-it-support\nPublished: N/A\nAuthor: N/A\nHighlights:\nThis course is part of Google IT Support Professional Certificate\n...\nTaught in English\n...\n11 languages available\n...\nThis course is part of the Google IT Support Professional Certificate\n\n---\n\nTitle: Google IT Support Professional Certificate | Coursera\nURL: https://www.coursera.org/professional-certificates/google-it-support?adgroupid=88979276353&adposition=&campaignid=1855233775&creativeid=408459231277&device=c&devicemodel=&hide_mobile_promo=&keyword=&matchtype=&network=g\nPublished: N/A\nAuthor: N/A\nHighlights:\nGoogle IT Support Professional Certificate | Coursera\n...\nSupport Professional Certificate\n...\nTaught in English\n...\n6 languages available\n\n---\n\nTitle: Translations for course content - the Coursera Support Center\nURL: https://www.coursera.support/s/article/learner-000002049\nPublished: N/A\nAuthor: N/A\nHighlights:\nYou can select your preferred language using the drop-down menu at the top right of your screen to find translated learning content. You can follow these steps ...\n\n---\n\nTitle: Google IT Support Professional Certificate | Coursera\nURL: https://www.coursera.org/professional-certificates/google-it-support?adgroupid=90913850130&adpostion=&campaignid=9433689805&creativeid=419672914461&device=c&devicemodel=&hide_mobile_promo=&keyword=it+support+courses&matchtype=p&network=g\nPublished: N/A\nAuthor: N/A\nHighlights:\nGoogle IT Support Professional Certificate | Coursera\n...\nSupport Professional Certificate\n...\nTaught in English\n...\n6 languages available",
